title: CodeOne
extract: Code 1: A time critical case with a lights and sirens ambulance response. An example is a cardiac arrest or serious traffic accident. Code 2: An acute but non-time critical response. The ambulance does not use lights and sirens to respond. ... Code 1: A time critical event with response requiring lights and siren.
